videos.description: Josh Allen pass complete to Tanner Gentry for 28 yds to the Wyom 39 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: Great throw and catch for Wyoming on their opening drive for a gain of 28

videos.description: Jamaal Williams run for 36 yds to the Wyom 40 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: Jamaal Williams's huge run sets up BYU in Wyoming territory

videos.description: Jamaal Williams run for 23 yds to the Wyom 17 Jamaal Williams fumbled, recovered by Wyom Lucas Wacha
videos.headline: J. Williams run for 23 yds,J. Williams fumbled, recovered by Wyom L. Wacha

videos.description: TEAM run for a loss of 20 yards to the Wyom 3 TEAM fumbled, recovered by Wyom Dalton Fields
videos.headline: Weather playing a factor early on as Wyoming botches a punt leading to great field position for BYU

videos.description: Tanner Mangum drops back to throw, but he decides to keep it himself and runs in for the touchdown to give BYU a 7-0 lead over Wyoming.
videos.headline: BYU scores opening touchdown of Poinsettia Bowl

videos.description: Tanner Mangum tries to find an open receiver, but Wyoming's Andrew Wingard picks off the pass, giving the Cowboys the ball back.
videos.headline: Mangum picked off by Wyoming defense

videos.description: BYU Head Coach Kalani Sitake on how to deal with the wet conditions in the 2nd half
videos.headline: BYU Head Coach Kalani Sitake on how to deal with the wet conditions in the 2nd half

videos.description: Brian Hill gets the handoff and rushes for the four-yard touchdown to cut BYU's lead over Wyoming to 10-7.
videos.headline: Wyoming gets on the board with rushing TD

videos.description: Tanner Mangum pass complete to Jonah Trinnaman for 39 yds to the Wyom 5 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: T. Mangum pass,to J. Trinnaman for 39 yds for a 1ST down

videos.description: Tanner Mangum's pass is initially tipped by a few different players, but it falls into the hands of Tanner Balderree to give the Cougars a touchdown and 17-7 lead.
videos.headline: BYU gets TD off tipped pass to increase lead

videos.description: Josh Allen pass intercepted Dayan Lake return for 14 yds to the BYU 45
videos.headline: J. Allen pass intercepted,D. Lake return  for 14 yds

videos.description: Jamaal Williams gets the ball and takes off 36 yards for the touchdown to give BYU a 24-7 lead over Wyoming.
videos.headline: Williams' big run pads BYU's bowl lead

videos.description: Josh Allen pass complete to Tanner Gentry for 9 yds for a TD
videos.headline: J. Allen pass,to T. Gentry for 9 yds for a TD

videos.description: Jamaal Williams run for 30 yds to the Wyom 45 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: J. Williams run for 30 yds for a 1ST down

videos.description: Josh Allen finds Tanner Gentry for the 23-yard touchdown to reduce BYU's lead over Wyoming to 24-21.
videos.headline: Wyoming cuts into BYU's lead with 23-yard TD pass

videos.description: With Wyoming trying to take the lead in the Poinsettia Bowl, Josh Allen throws downfield, but it is intercepted by BYU's Kai Nacua, which seals the deal for the Cougars.
videos.headline: BYU's INT seals Poinsettia Bowl victory

videos.description: BYU coach Kalani Sitake breaks down his team's victory over Wyoming to win the Poinsettia Bowl.
videos.headline: Sitake happy BYU seniors could go out with bowl win

videos.description: Postgame breakdown and trophy ceremony for BYU's 24-21 victory over Wyoming
videos.headline: Postgame breakdown and trophy ceremony for BYU's 24-21 victory over Wyoming
